bilingual.source: She is fully aware of the risks involved.
bilingual.target: 她完全地意识到了所涉及的风险。

bilingual.source: The project is fully funded by the government.
bilingual.target: 这个项目完全地由政府资助。

bilingual.source: The room was fully furnished when they moved in.
bilingual.target: 当他们搬进去时，房间已经完全地配备了家具。

bilingual.source: He needs to fully recover before returning to work.
bilingual.target: 他需要完全地康复后才能重返工作。

bilingual.source: He fully understands the consequences of his actions.
bilingual.target: 他完全地理解了自己行为的后果。

bilingual.source: By communing with others, you learn to love yourself more fully.
bilingual.target: 通过与他人沟通, 你学会更完全地爱自己.

bilingual.source: Doctors are required to fully inform a patient about his or her illness.
bilingual.target: 要求医生对患者的疾病完全地告知。

bilingual.source: Joy begins to enter the dance as one ascends more fully to 3000 strands of DNA.
bilingual.target: 当你更完全地提升到3000股DNA时，欢乐就开始进入舞蹈。

bilingual.source: When you fully love someone, you identify with and youbecome one with that one.
bilingual.target: 当完全地爱某人，你认为自己就是他并且成为了他。

bilingual.source: Who can fully know the infinite God? and what need is there of knowing the Infinite?
bilingual.target: 谁能完全地明白无限的神呢？有什么必要去了解无限呢？

list.abstract: fully是一个英语单词，可以用作副词，可以翻译为充分地、完全地，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Though some dryers are much better than others, just make sure you dry them fully, and it shouldn't be a major problem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然有些烘手机比较好，只要确保你完全地擦干手，应该就没什么大问题。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm fully aware they're alive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我当然知道她们是有生命的。

yingyinNormal.en: Harvard and Radcliffe was fully integrated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哈佛和拉德克利夫完全统一了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Spock. You are fully capable of deciding your own destiny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯波克，你完全能够决定自己的命运。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you fully grown? No. I believe he's just a boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你长成熟了吗？还没。我想他只是个男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: And by the time they are fully trained, so will you be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等它们训练有素之时，你们的训练也完成了。

yingyinNormal.en: Now the south has been subdued, and our forces are fully armed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今南方已定，兵甲已足，

yingyinNormal.en: She will be 50 feet long when fully grown. Bigger than the T. Rex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 成熟后她将有50英尺长，比霸王龙体型还要大。

yingyinNormal.en: See there are still several areas that haven't been fully excavated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为里面还有些地区还没完全开挖的。

yingyinNormal.en: Once an idea has taken hold of the brain, it's almost impossible to eradicate. An idea that is fully formed, fully understood, that sticks. Right in there somewhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一旦扎根 根深蒂固盘亘脑海。

yingyinNormal.en: SpaceX is currently developing a fully and rapidly reusable launch system.
yingyinNormal.zh: SpaceX公司目前正在研发一种充分快速的可重复使用的运载系统。

yingyinNormal.en: Claire, why is there a fully cooked turkey in the backpack we left at your house?
yingyinNormal.zh: 克莱尔，我们落在你家的背包里怎么突然多了一只烤好的火鸡？

yingyinNormal.en: I see I'm not needed to lend you strength. You're fully in command of the argument.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来我不需要助你一臂之力，你完全能控制得住局势。

yingyinNormal.en: Tiberius, this is going to sound completely horrible but, I do not fully trust you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 提比略，虽然这听上去很糟，但是，我不全信你。

yingyinNormal.en: When fully operational, it'll become the world's most powerful telescope of its class.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当其全面投运，将会是世界上同类望远镜中的翘楚。

yingyinNormal.en: No, Homo habilis was erect. Australopithecus was never fully erect. Well, maybe he was nervous.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，能人是直立行走（与“勃起”同词）的，南方古猿不是完全直立行走的。或许他是紧张罢了。

yingyinNormal.en: Not many first-year students could take on a a fully grown mountain troll and live to tell the tale.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一年级新生能勇斗山中巨怪，还保住性命，这事可不多见。

yingyinNormal.en: OK, a fully equipped ambulance, Molly can examine me on the way, it'll save time. Ready to go, Molly?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，有了装备齐全的救护车，茉莉可以在路上给我做检查，省点时间。准备好了吗，茉莉 ？

yingyinNormal.en: I now need you to acknowledge receipt of the package so that I'm fully indemnified and no longer liable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在要你确认收到包裹我才算完整履行法律义务。

yingyinNormal.en: Damn! They got big. Yeah, they fully mature on the flight out. So the proprioceptive sims seem to work really well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 靠，他们真是巨大。是啊，他们已经完全成熟了，看来模拟化身运作良好。
